high_descs: Walk forward to the counter then turn left.
Pick up the spatula that's in front of you.
Turn right and move to your right until you face the sink.
Wash the spatula in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and walk just past the dish washer then turn left.
Put the spatula on the counter near the edge to the right of the dish washer horizontally so it runs along the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula on the counter.

high_descs: go forward to the counter and turn to the left facing the counter
pick up the spatula from the counter top
turn to the right twice and go to the front of the sink and turn to the left and go to the sink
put the spatula in the sink and turn on the water to fill the sink and turn off and drain the water and pick up the spatula from the sink
turn to the left twice and take a few steps and turn to the left and go to the counter and turn to the left and go to the counter
put the spatula on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spatula on the counter top

high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter, then turn left to face the toaster.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the spatula in the sink.
Place the spatula on the counter, near the edge, in front of and to the right of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spatula on a counter.
